sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Browser as Web Browser
    participant DashRoute as Dashboard Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+ OAuth
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant NBController as Notebook Controller<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant NBRoute as Notebook Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+ OAuth
    participant Jupyter as JupyterLab<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.2+
    participant KServe as KServe Controller<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelCtrl as Model Controller<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>TLS 1.3
    participant Knative as Knative Activator<br/>8012/TCP mTLS
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP mTLS
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prom: Workflow 1: Model Development to Deployment

    User->>Browser: Access platform
    Browser->>DashRoute: GET /<br/>Auth: OAuth Bearer
    DashRoute->>Dashboard: Forward request<br/>Validated session
    Dashboard-->>Browser: Platform UI

    User->>Dashboard: Launch Jupyter notebook
    Dashboard->>NBController: POST /api/notebooks<br/>Create Notebook CR
    NBController->>NBController: Create StatefulSet<br/>Create Route<br/>Inject OAuth proxy
    NBController-->>Dashboard: Notebook created

    User->>NBRoute: Access notebook<br/>Auth: OAuth Bearer
    NBRoute->>Jupyter: Forward (OAuth validated)
    Jupyter-->>User: JupyterLab interface

    User->>Jupyter: Develop & train model
    Jupyter->>S3: PUT /models/model.pkl<br/>AWS IAM Auth
    S3-->>Jupyter: Model uploaded

    User->>Dashboard: Create InferenceService
    Dashboard->>KServe: POST InferenceService CR
    KServe->>KServe: Create Knative Service<br/>Configure autoscaling
    KServe->>ModelCtrl: Notify (watch event)
    ModelCtrl->>ModelCtrl: Create Route<br/>Create VirtualService<br/>Create AuthConfig

    Predictor->>S3: GET /models/model.pkl<br/>Storage initializer<br/>AWS IAM Auth
    S3-->>Predictor: Model artifacts
    Predictor->>Predictor: Load model into memory

    Note over User,Prom: Inference Request Flow

    User->>Gateway: POST /v2/models/model/infer<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>Gateway: TLS termination<br/>JWT validation
    Gateway->>Knative: Forward via mTLS<br/>Service identity
    Knative->>Predictor: Inference request<br/>mTLS (service mesh)
    Predictor->>Predictor: Run inference
    Predictor->>TrustyAI: Send inference data<br/>HTTP payload processor
    Predictor-->>Knative: Prediction result
    Knative-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: JSON response

    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Calculate fairness metrics<br/>Detect bias
    TrustyAI->>Prom: Export metrics<br/>ServiceMonitor
    Prom->>TrustyAI: GET /metrics

    Note over User,Prom: Distributed Training Job

    User->>Jupyter: Submit PyTorchJob
    Jupyter->>KServe: kubectl apply PyTorchJob CR
    activate KServe
    KServe->>Kueue: Create Workload CR<br/>Request resources
    Kueue->>Kueue: Evaluate quotas<br/>Check cluster capacity
    Kueue-->>KServe: Workload admitted
    KServe->>KServe: Create PodGroup<br/>Create master pod<br/>Create worker pods
    deactivate KServe

    Note over Predictor,S3: Training pods communicate (port 23456)<br/>Save checkpoints to S3

    Note over User,Prom: ML Pipeline Execution

    User->>Dashboard: Create pipeline
    Dashboard->>DSPO: DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR
    DSPO->>DSPO: Deploy API Server<br/>Deploy Argo Controller<br/>Deploy MariaDB
    User->>Dashboard: Submit pipeline run
    Dashboard->>ArgoAPI: POST /api/v1/workflows
    ArgoAPI->>MariaDB: Store metadata<br/>MySQL/3306
    ArgoAPI->>ArgoCtrl: Create Workflow CR
    ArgoCtrl->>ArgoCtrl: Create pipeline pods

    Note over Predictor,S3: Pipeline pods execute tasks<br/>Log artifacts to S3 and MariaDB

    participant ArgoAPI as Pipeline API Server
    participant ArgoCtrl as Argo Controller
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB
    participant DSPO as DSP Operator
    participant Kueue as Kueue
